    <title><![CDATA[使用hexo写Blog，并发布到github]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.wiflish.com/2014/02/26/hexo%E5%86%99blog%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%88%B0github/"/>
    <id>http://blog.wiflish.com/2014/02/26/hexo写blog，并发布到github/</id>
    <published>2014-02-26T01:26:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-02-26T01:47:37.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="-nodejs">安装nodejs</h2>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>下载<a href="http://nodejs.org/download/" target="_blank">nodejs</a>，选择对应的操作系统版本。</li>
<li>安装，一路next。 </li>
<li>打开cmd窗口，输入： node -v </li>
<li>正确显示nodejs的版本号，即安装成功。</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="-hexo">安装hexo</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>安装hexo，根据网络状况需要一定的时间</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="blockquote">&gt; npm install hexo -g</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>初始化blog.</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>&gt; $ hexo init blog && <span class="built_in">cd</span> blog
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>创建blog文章</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>&gt; $ hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="string">"Hello World"</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>启动服务器,输入：<a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank">http://localhost:4000</a> 访问之.</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>&gt; <span class="variable">$ </span>hexo server
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装主题，hexo主题列表： <a href="https://github.com/tommy351/hexo/wiki/Themes" target="_blank">Themes</a></p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>cd %BLOG_PATH
$ git clone <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">repository</span>&gt;</span> themes/<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">theme-name</span>&gt;</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</blockquote>
<h2 id="-github">部署到github</h2>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>下载安装<a href="https://code.google.com/p/msysgit/downloads/list" target="_blank">git</a>。</li>
<li>在github申请账号，并创建一个username.github.io的仓库名（username为你的账号名）.</li>
<li>根据github官方帮助文档,<a href="https://help.github.com/articles/generating-ssh-keys" target="_blank">安装SSH KEYS</a></li>
<li>进入上述的blog目录，打开_config.yml文件，修改deploy段配置，详见：<a href="http://zespia.tw/hexo/docs/deployment.html" target="_blank">Hexo Deployment</a></li>
<li>部署到github<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="comment">hexo</span> <span class="comment">deploy</span> <span class="literal">-</span><span class="literal">-</span><span class="comment">或者</span> <span class="comment">hexo</span> <span class="comment">d</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="-">参考</h2>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="http://ibruce.info/2013/11/22/hexo-your-blog/" target="_blank">http://ibruce.info/2013/11/22/hexo-your-blog/</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
    
    
